channel.title: Tar Filled Veins - Hern [Experimental]
channel.description:
New single from my upcoming EP, Reflection. This one mostly features samples of myself, though there is also a sample of the intro to Sour Apple by the band Dope Body (great band btw) featured prominently throughout the track.
Link is here: https://soundcloud.com/hernmusicofficial/7-1-a
Hope you enjoy, constructive criticism is welcome as always.
